text: Bangalaia fisheri is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1936. It is known from Gabon, the Ivory Coast, and Equatorial Guinea.BioLib.cz - Bangalaia fisheri. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Prosopocerini Category:Beetles described in 1936
